<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFCEFFAB61FDFE45C49DFE2B" author="Rao, G. C. &amp; Ganapati, G." box="[186,454,403,430]" pageId="2" pageNumber="303" pagination="82 - 125" refId="ref13546" refString="Rao, G. C. &amp; Ganapati, G. (1968) The interstitial fauna inhabiting the beach sands of Waltair coast. Proceedings of the National Institute of Sciences of India, B, 34, 82 - 125." type="journal article" year="1968">Rao &amp; Ganapati (1968)</bibRefCitation>
